HI,<br>
I think the OSM code is GPL see the license here<br>
<a href="http://trac.openstreetmap.org/browser/LICENSE?rev=18108" target="_blank">http://trac.openstreetmap.org/browser/LICENSE?rev=18108</a> not AGPL, and<br>
neither of them are allowed to be included into a LGPLed project, only<br>
LGPL is allowed to be included into AGPL and GPL.<br>
<br>
and the header should look like this,<br>
<a href="http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html#SEC4" target="_blank">http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html#SEC4</a><br>
<br>
But the Wikipeida map layers  has moved to SlippyMap.js see this<br>
commit  <a href="http://www.mail-archive.com/mediawiki-cvs@.../msg08963.html" target="_blank">http://www.mail-archive.com/mediawiki-cvs@.../msg08963.html</a><br>
